# 🛡️ KeyShield v3.0

### All-in-One Input Security Monitor

**Detect keyloggers, rootkits, input hooks, clipboard hijackers, screen capture tools,
DLL/.so injection, BadUSB devices, network exfiltration, and persistence mechanisms.**

