## ✨ Features

<table>
<tr>
<td width="50%">

### 🔍 Detection Engine
- **12 specialized detectors** working in parallel
- **Known signature database** with 30+ keylogger families
- **Behavioral heuristics** with tiered keyword scoring
- **Self-exclusion** — never flags itself as a threat
- **Finding deduplication** — no duplicate alerts
- **Cross-platform** — Windows, Linux, macOS

</td>
<td width="50%">

### 🖥️ User Interface
- **Web GUI** — dark cybersecurity dashboard
- **CLI** — full-featured command-line interface
- **Python API** — integrate into your own tools
- **Real-time progress** via Server-Sent Events
- **Auto-launches browser** for beginners
- **Report export** — JSON, TXT, CSV

</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>

### 🛡️ Security Features
- **MITRE ATT&CK mapped** — every finding has a technique ID
- **Threat scoring** — CLEAN → LOW → MEDIUM → HIGH → CRITICAL
- **Scan profiles** — quick, standard, paranoid
- **Configurable whitelist** — reduce false positives
- **Log integrity** — rotating log files with timestamps
- **Path traversal protection** on report downloads

</td>
<td>

### 🔧 Architecture
- **Modular detector system** — add new detectors easily
- **BaseDetector pattern** — shared self-exclusion logic
- **Thread-safe web server** — proper locking on shared state
- **Configuration system** — `~/.keyshield/config.json`
- **Robust error handling** — detectors fail independently
- **Zero external dependencies** beyond `psutil` and `flask`

</td>
</tr>
</table>

