## 🔍 Detection Modules

KeyShield includes **12 specialized detectors**, each targeting a different attack vector:

### Core Detectors

| # | Detector | Description | MITRE ATT&CK |
|---|----------|-------------|---------------|
| 1 | 🔑 **Keylogger Detector** | Known keylogger signatures (30+ families) + behavioral heuristics | [T1056.001](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1056/001/) |
| 2 | 🪝 **Hook Detector** | Win: DLL hooks · Linux: LD_PRELOAD, ptrace, xinput, /dev/input | [T1056.001](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1056/001/), [T1574.006](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1574/006/), [T1055.008](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1055/008/) |
| 3 | ⚙️ **Process Detector** | Parent-child analysis, duplicate detection, recently spawned | [T1055](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1055/), [T1059](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1059/) |
| 4 | 📋 **Clipboard Monitor** | Clipboard hijacking detection + rapid-change monitoring | [T1115](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1115/) |
| 5 | 📸 **Screen Capture Detector** | Win: GDI capture · Linux: framebuffer + screen tools | [T1113](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1113/) |
| 6 | 🌐 **Network Exfil Detector** | C2 ports, suspicious connections, DNS tunneling | [T1041](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1041/), [T1048.003](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1048/003/) |

### Advanced Detectors

| # | Detector | Description | MITRE ATT&CK |
|---|----------|-------------|---------------|
| 7 | 💉 **DLL/SO Injection** | Win: malicious DLLs · Linux: /proc/maps .so analysis | [T1055.001](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1055/001/), [T1055.009](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1055/009/) |
| 8 | 🔄 **Persistence Detector** | Win: Registry/Startup · Linux: cron/systemd · macOS: LaunchAgent | [T1547.001](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1547/001/), [T1053.003](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1053/003/) |
| 9 | 🧠 **Memory Scanner** | Fileless malware indicators, memory anomalies | [T1055](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1055/) |
| 10 | 🐧 **Kernel Module Detector** | Rootkit kernel modules, hidden modules, tainted kernel | [T1014](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1014/) |
| 11 | 🔌 **USB HID Detector** | BadUSB, Rubber Ducky, O.MG Cable, multiple keyboards | [T1200](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1200/) |
| 12 | ⏰ **Scheduled Task Detector** | Win: Task Scheduler · Linux: crontab/systemd timers | [T1053.005](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1053/005/), [T1053.003](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1053/003/) |

