## 🗺️ MITRE ATT&CK Coverage

KeyShield maps findings to the [MITRE ATT&CK Framework](https://attack.mitre.org/):

```
Tactic                    Technique                    Detector
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Collection                T1056.001 Keylogging         Keylogger, Hook
Collection                T1115 Clipboard Data         Clipboard Monitor
Collection                T1113 Screen Capture         Screen Capture
Credential Access         T1056.001 Input Capture      Keylogger, Hook
Defense Evasion           T1014 Rootkit                Kernel Module
Defense Evasion           T1055 Process Injection      DLL/SO Injection, Memory
Defense Evasion           T1055.001 DLL Injection      DLL Injection
Defense Evasion           T1055.008 Ptrace Injection   Hook Detector
Defense Evasion           T1055.009 Proc Mem Inject    SO Injection
Defense Evasion           T1055.012 Process Hollowing  Process Detector
Execution                 T1059 Command Interpreter    Process Detector
Exfiltration              T1041 Exfil Over C2          Network Exfil
Exfiltration              T1048.003 DNS Exfiltration   Network Exfil
Initial Access            T1200 Hardware Additions     USB HID
Persistence               T1053.003 Cron               Scheduled Task
Persistence               T1053.005 Scheduled Task     Scheduled Task
Persistence               T1547.001 Registry Run Keys  Persistence
Persistence               T1574.006 LD_PRELOAD         Hook Detector
```

