## 🧪 Testing

```bash
# Run all tests
python -m pytest tests/ -v

# Run with coverage
python -m pytest tests/ --cov=keyshield --cov-report=html

# Run specific test file
python -m pytest tests/test_engine.py -v

# Run specific test
python -m pytest tests/test_engine.py::TestConfig::test_self_exclusion -v
```

### Test Files

| File | Coverage |
|------|----------|
| `tests/test_engine.py` | ScanEngine, ScanResult, Finding, dedup |
| `tests/test_config.py` | Config, whitelist, profiles, self-exclusion |
| `tests/test_detectors.py` | All 12 detectors return valid results |
| `tests/test_web.py` | Flask routes, API endpoints, SSE |

